---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: 所有 DeepSeek 技術文章與應用教學檔案庫
description: 瀏覽所有關於 DeepSeek (深度求索) 的繁體中文技術指南、API 整合方案、提示詞優化技巧及香港本地數字轉型精選案例。
pagination:
  data: collections.posts
  size: 10
  alias: posts
  reverse: true
permalink: "/posts/{% if pagination.pageNumber > 0 %}page-{{ pagination.pageNumber + 1 }}/{% endif %}index.html"
---
<style>
  .archive-layout-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 17fr 7fr; gap: 40px; }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .archive-layout-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  
  .archive-header { padding: 20px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; margin-bottom: 30px; }
  .archive-card { padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #edf2f7; border-radius: 6px; margin-bottom: 20px; background: #fff; }
  .archive-card h3 { margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 18px; }
  .archive-card h3 a { color: #2d3748; text-decoration: none; }
  .archive-card h3 a:hover { color: #0066cc; }
  .archive-date { font-size: 13px; color: #a0aec0; display: block; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  
  .page-link { padding: 6px 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd; text-decoration: none; color: #0066cc; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 14px; }
  .page-active { padding: 6px 12px; background: #333; color: #fff; border: 1px solid #333; font-weight: bold; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 14px; }
</style>

<header class="archive-header">
  <h1 style="font-size: 26px; color: #111; margin: 0 0 10px 0;">DeepSeek 繁體中文全量文章檔案庫</h1>
  <p style="color:#666; margin:0;">這裏匯集了本站發布的所有關於 DeepSeek 模型的深度剖析、本地化私有部署與商業落地實踐指南。</p>
</header>

<div class="archive-layout-grid">
  <div class="archive-list">
    {% for post in posts %}
      <article class="archive-card">
        <span class="archive-date">發布日期：{{ post.date | dateFilter }}</span>
        <h3><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
        <p style="font-size:14px; color:#4a5568; line-height:1.6;">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        <a href="{{ post.url }}" style="font-size:13px; font-weight:bold; text-decoration:none; color:#0066cc;">閱讀全文 &middot; 掌握技術精髓 &raquo;</a>
      </article>
    {% else %}
      <p>精準技術指南正在加載中，請稍候回來查看。</p>
    {% endfor %}

    {% if pagination.pages.length > 1 %}
    <nav class="pagination-nav" style="margin-top: 40px; text-align: center;">
      <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: inline-flex; gap: 8px; align-items: center;">
        <li>
          {% if pagination.href.previous %}
            <a href="{{ pagination.href.previous }}" class="page-link">&laquo; 上一頁</a>
          {% else %}
            <span style="padding: 6px 12px; border: 1px solid #eee; color: #ccc; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 14px;">&laquo; 上一頁</span>
          {% endif %}
        </li>
        {%- for pageEntry in pagination.pages %}
          <li>
            {% if page.url == pagination.hrefs[loop.index0] %}
              <span class="page-active">{{ loop.index }}</span>
            {% else %}
              <a href="{{ pagination.hrefs[loop.index0] }}" class="page-link">{{ loop.index }}</a>
            {% endif %}
          </li>
        {%- endfor %}
        <li>
          {% if pagination.href.next %}
            <a href="{{ pagination.href.next }}" class="page-link">下一頁 &raquo;</a>
          {% else %}
            <span style="padding: 6px 12px; border: 1px solid #eee; color: #ccc; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 14px;">下一頁 &raquo;</span>
          {% endif %}
        </li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
    {% endif %}
  </div>

  <aside class="archive-sidebar" style="background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; height: fit-content;">
    <h3 style="margin-top:0; font-size:16px; border-left:4px solid #0066cc; padding-left:10px; margin-bottom:15px;">⚡ 實時更新情報</h3>
    <ul style="list-style:none; padding:0; margin:0; line-height:2.2; font-size:14px;">
      {% for item in collections.posts | limit(5) %}
        <li style="white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis;"><a href="{{ item.url }}" style="color:#333; text-decoration:none;">{{ item.data.title }}</a></li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </aside>
</div>